   <narrative xml:lang="EN">CEF IV Project</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">China Environment Fund IV, L.P. (CEF IV or the Fund) is a ten-year private equity fund that will invest in the environmental sustainability and resource efficiency sectors. The Fund is targeting $ 350 million in commitments and will be managed by Tsing Capital Venture Capital Management Co. Ltd. (Tsing Capital or the Fund Manager).</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project is designed to have significant impact in (1) promotion of greenhouse gas reduction, (2) promotion of the more environmentally sustainable practices, (3) support of the development of a relatively new sector and (4) job creation, including in China&apos;s frontier regions, through investment in China-focused cleantech portfolio companies.</narrative>
  </description>
